column_.text_: Ahhh, we finally made it back. But what're we gonna do now?
I think... we should start by finding Rolan's house.

If memory serves, he was living at the church. But why the sudden
interest?
The church. Got it.

Dang, he didn't even answer you... Guess we still need to
work on his people skills.

Well, at least we know where he went. We should go see
what he's thinking.
Hey, it's everyone's favorite crew! Perfect timing, as usual.

Truth is, I just put out an urgent cry for help. We got a caravan
strong-armed by goblins in Skywyrm Valley!

I'm looking for folks to beat off the half-beasts and retrieve the
stolen goods.
Might be a tough battle, but think you can head out now?
Yeah.
No.
Yeah.
Knew I could count on you... Take care of yourselves, you hear?
No.

Preparation's the key to success. Just give me a holler when you're
ready.
You ready to make those goblins cough up what they stole?
Have you seen what's in this journal we found?
It's gotta be Rolan's, right? Could tell us how to rescue him.
My thoughts exactly. Maybe there's more of them out there.
Another one of Rolan's journals? Goes back pretty far into his past.
This journal seems more recent.
Another journal. But it's seen better days.
This journal was written by an "Astraeus." We're on the right track.
Look at how thick this one is. Guess Rolan had a lot to say.
We've got a whole library of Fix It Dude's journals now. Have ya read 'em all yet?
I've got news. Meet me at the church.
